{"tid":2446754,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不知道從什麼時候開始，在什麼東西上面都有個日期","createTime":"2021-03-14T16:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T06:03:42.000Z","uid":143093,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e57639b3005741f27ccd391eff63ec4cb437dc60","tid":2446754,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"我們分手的那天是4月1號，所以我一直當她們是開玩笑，我願意讓她們這個玩笑維持一個月。從分手的那一天開始，我每天買一罐4月1號到期的izone專輯，因為izone專輯是izone最愛的東西，而4月1號是她們的解散日子。我告訴我自己，當我買滿30張的時候，她們如果還不回來，這段感情就會過期。"},{"pid":"2b6108310d2c6d6e88b077b598680d5a3722c0c6","tid":2446754,"uid":143093,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:47:05.000Z","msg":"不知道從什麼時候開始，在什麼東西上面都有個日期，Kpop團會過期，izone會過期，連12女孩都會過期，我開始懷疑，在這個世界上，還有什麼東西是不會過期的?"},{"pid":"970cb08cadd296ac60f3f327586a314286c67dad","tid":2446754,"uid":143093,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:47:30.000Z","msg":"其實了解一個人並不代表什麼，人是會變的，今天他喜歡izone，明天他可以喜歡別的🚬🚬"},{"pid":"d62b3e82741012cc2d464c259d73a8769244ed04","tid":2446754,"uid":344464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T17:30:42.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96902bfacc1353cad6fb127c4fdae8bd83a8432c","tid":2446754,"uid":25924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"😭"},{"pid":"79cf24c0ee0ad9d75dfcaa39b34b0ba1b4baf058","tid":2446754,"uid":143093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T17:35:09.000Z","msg":"終於在一家CD店，讓我找到第30張izone專輯。就在4月1號的早晨，我開始明白一件事情，在izone的心中，我和這張izone專輯沒有什麼分別。"},{"pid":"a6fd77c6a97d86de29867606d0c390ce9a0cf9d1","tid":2446754,"uid":143093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"96902bfacc1353cad6fb127c4fdae8bd83a8432c","tid":2446754,"uid":25924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"😭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":